## ğŸš€ Getting Started

Create your first CLI app:

```python
from sayer import Sayer, Option

app = Sayer()

@app.command()
def hello(name: str = Option(..., help="Your name")):
    """Say hello to someone"""
    print(f"Hello, {name}!")

if __name__ == "__main__":
    app()
```

Run it:

```bash
$ python app.py hello --name Ada
Hello, Ada!
```

